snippet.textDisplay: Thank you for making this. I have my doubts about the vaccine and when they are allowing athletes to do contact sports with no isolation, masks or washing hands before touching the sports equipment, i.e. football , baseball etc, then wht are they held to a different standard than everyone else? Except for the greed of the team owners who don't value their employees' lives over money. But you lay out a logical scenario in your video and I shared it on Facebook and Linked In for a combined total of 9000 contacts. Hope this helps to get the word out. One thing, please don't talj so fast. It's a lot of information and I know you wnt to convey it but when you go too fast speaking, people need time to processes you're saying before the next point comes barreling at them. Good job!
